data.title: CHFI Secret Voices: Round 11
data.meta_description: Imagine winning loads of CASH just for knowing some famous voices!  98.1 CHFI brings YOU another easy way to win BIG $$$ with
data.text:
Guess all 5 of our famous voices, saying “CHFI, Toronto’s Perfect Music Mix”, for your chance to WIN CASH!

JACKPOT: Identify all 5 voices, in the correct order, and you’ll WIN the whole CHFI Secret Voices jackpot!

BONUS: If you’re the first person to guess one of the voices, you’ll win $1000 for each correct voice! Guess the voices – WIN CASH!

Play weekdays at 7AM, 8AM, 11AM, 1PM , & 4PM! Just listen for the keyword to text to 981981* with your name to play…

CHFI Secret Voices Round 11 Jackpot is: $111,250
